    AdaptyUIPaywallView view, 
    AdaptyProfile profile
) { }
```

<Details>
<summary>イベント例（クリックして展開）</summary>

h3-user-generated-events-p246e1b58.translation:
```javascript
{
  "profile": {
    "accessLevels": {
      "premium": {
        "id": "premium",
        "isActive": true,
        "expiresAt": "2024-02-15T10:30:00Z"
      }
    },
    "subscriptions": [
      {
        "vendorProductId": "premium_monthly",
        "isActive": true,
        "expiresAt": "2024-02-15T10:30:00Z"
